This is still experimental and OS X support will be prioritized after Linux. The contributions welcome label is intended to suggest that the core team is not likely to work on this feature. We are hoping to get MKL running on OS X which will add a significant performance boost.

This is still experimental and OS X support will be prioritized after Linux.  The contributions welcome label is intended to suggest that the core team is not likely to work on this feature.  We are hoping to get MKL running on OS X which will add a significant performance boost.
